Package com.mygdx.game.gameLogic.Characters

Contains the classes for all the characters and objects in the game.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CharacterInfo
    Provides an interface to query information about the character
    EnemyInfo
    Provides the interface to provide information aobut the enemy
    HeroInfo
    Interface to query hero specific information
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Character
    Class that represents world characters such as the player controlled hero and the enemies.
    Enemy
    base class that implements enemies in the game
    EnemyFlying
    class that implements ground based enemies
    EnemyGround
    class that implements flying type enemies
    Entity
    Basic object fields and methods.
    Hero
    Class that represents the player controlled character.
    HeroLifesWrapper
    Wrapper used on hero to use the lifes and immunity features.
    Light
    The light used around around the hero and the rechargers.
    Platform
    Class that implements a platform.
    Recharger
    Class that represents the recharger item.
